milies over the past few decades.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 0aAfrican American families. 0aDivorcezUnited States. 0aFamilieszUnited States. 0aMarriagezUnited States. 0aRemarriagezUnited States. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Sociology / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.4159/9780674029491zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780674029491423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780674029491/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_SN  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK